Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Gives the slotted power a chance to inflict moderate negative energy damage and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.    This effect will trigger roughly 5 times per minute.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Corruptors and may be slotted into any Corruptor damage power.
DisplayName: Superior Attuned Superior Malice of the Corruptor F
SubName: Set: Superior Malice of the Corruptor
